OL,3,CHousing Executive rents to increase in
OL,4,CApril
OL,6,FHousing Executive rents are to
OL,7,Fincrease by 7.7% from the start of
OL,8,FApril.
OL,10,FThe Housing Executive said each tenant
OL,11,Fwill receive a letter over the next
OL,12,Ffew weeks advising of their new rent
OL,13,Fcharges, and what they need to do.
OL,15,FA Department for Communities statement
OL,16,Fsaid rent pays for the housing
OL,17,Fservices provided by the executive,
OL,18,FNorthern Ireland's public housing
OL,19,Fauthority.
