OL,6,FThe statement said: "This rent
OL,7,Fincrease will provide funding for
OL,8,Fessential maintenance, improvements
OL,9,Fand investment, while also keeping the
OL,10,Frent affordable for tenants.
OL,12,F"Tenant affordability was once again
OL,13,Fthe department's key consideration;
OL,14,F79% of Housing Executive tenants are
OL,15,Fcurrently in receipt of housing
OL,16,Fassistance.
OL,18,F"These tenants will be protected from
OL,19,Fthe impact of the rent increase."
