OL,3,CHousing Executive rents to increase in
OL,4,CApril
OL,6,F"Housing Executive rent levels are
OL,7,Fconsidered every year by taking into
OL,8,Faccount a wide range of factors,
OL,9,Fincluding: inflation; projected
OL,10,Frunning costs; spending requirements
OL,11,Fand affordability."
OL,13,FThe increase equates to an average
OL,14,Fadditional #5.72 per week, increasing
OL,15,Fthe average weekly rent for tenants
OL,16,Ffrom #74.24 to #79.96.
