OL,6,FGrainia Long, chief executive at the
OL,7,FHousing Executive, said: "Rent pays
OL,8,Ffor customer and neighbourhood
OL,9,Fservices as well as all maintenance of
OL,10,Four homes and improvement work.
OL,12,F"It has never been more important that
OL,13,Fwe continue to invest in our homes and
OL,14,Fprovide services to tenants.
OL,16,F"The rent increase will go straight
OL,17,Fback into our houses and our customer
OL,18,Fservices.
