OL,6,F"This year we are spending #204million
OL,7,Fmaintaining and improving our homes
OL,8,Ffor our tenants and this increase will
OL,9,Fenable an increase in investment to
OL,10,Fapproximately #288million next year."
OL,12,FShe added: "We are very much aware of
OL,13,Fthe ongoing financial pressures faced
OL,14,Fby our tenants, and have increased the
OL,15,Fsize of our Financial Inclusion Team
OL,16,Fto ensure we have the right support in
OL,17,Fplace.
